@node IMTEXTURE
@{b}IMTEXTURE@{ub}

@{b}Template:@{ub}
 NAME/A,POS,ALIGN,SIZE,P1,P2,P3,P4,P5,P6,P7,P8,P9,P10,P11,P12,P13,P14,P15,P16,ACTOR
@{b}Arguments:@{ub}
 STRING NAME
   Name of Imagine texture file (no default).
 VECTOR POS
